Biografia Socrates Corinthians

Nome completo de socrates é Sócrates Brasileiro Sampaio de Souza
Viera de Oliveira, tinha um apelido de Doutor.
Nasceu em 19/02/1954 e morreu em 4/12/2011 aos 57 anos.

Socrates era um jogador de futebol de muito sucesso e muita classe, o inicio
de sua carreira foi no Botafogo-SP, onde teve 259 jogos e 101 gols, logo após foi para o corinthians em 1978 e ficou ate 1984, tendo 297 jogos e 172
gols, na seleção brasileira teve 62 jogos e 25 gols

Socrates era chamado de doutor não so pela classe e tecnica que tinha dentro de campo, mas também por ser formado em medicina.

Socrates venceu 3 campeonatos paulistas pelo corinthians e foi um dos principais idealizadores da democracia corinthiana

Socrates full name is Socrates Brasileiro Sampaio de Souza Vieira de Oliveira, but he had a surname Doutor.
He was born on 19/02/1954 and died on 4/12/2011 he had 57 years.

Socrates was a soccer player with so much sucess and a lot of class, the beginning of his career was in Botafogo-SP, where he had played 259 games and 101 goals, after that he went to Corinthians on 1978 and stayed until 1984, with 297 games and 172 goals, in the Brazil team he had played 62 games and have 25 goals

Socrates was called by doctor not just for his class and technic he had inside the pitch, but also because he was graduated in medicine

Socrates won 3 paulista championship and He was one of the pioneers of Corinthians democracy